{
  "$schema": "../schemas/solver-problem-ir.schema.json",
  "meta": {
    "problem_id": "tj-2026-nankai-yimo-25-alt-labels",
    "title": "25 题同构回归用例：替换点名与问题 id",
    "note": "本文件用于验证 SolverFamily 不依赖 D/M/N/F/G 或固定 question id。题意结构与南开 25 题同构，标准答案在 server/tests/solver/expected/ 中。"
  },
  "input": {
    "problem_id": "tj-2026-nankai-yimo-25-alt-labels",
    "pattern": "path-minimum",
    "problem_type": "quadratic_path_minimum",
    "original_text": {
      "source": "Method Solver V1 回归测试",
      "number": "25",
      "lines": [
        "已知抛物线 y＝ax²＋bx＋c（a＞0）与 y 轴交于点 C，且满足 2a＋b＝0，对称轴与 x 轴的交点为 T。",
        "（A）当 a＝2，c＝−5 时，求点 T 的坐标及抛物线的解析式；",
        "（B）设 U(m,1)（m＞2）在抛物线上，V 在抛物线上且在第四象限，∠UTV＝90°，TU＝TV。P 在线段 TU 上，R 在线段 UV 上，W 为 TV 的中点，且 TP＝√2·RV。",
        "① 当 UV＝√10 时，直接写出抛物线的解析式及 PR＋WR 的最小值；",
        "② 当 PR＋WR 的最小值为 5√10/2 时，求抛物线解析式及此时 R 的坐标。"
      ]
    },
    "symbols": ["x", "a", "b", "c", "m"],
    "symbol_roles": {
      "x": "function_variable",
      "a": "quadratic_coefficient",
      "b": "quadratic_coefficient",
      "c": "quadratic_coefficient",
      "m": "dynamic_parameter"
    },
    "constraints": {
      "a": ">0",
      "m": ">2"
    },
    "data": {
      "function": {
        "id": "parabola",
        "type": "quadratic",
        "expression": "a*x**2 + b*x + c",
        "coefficient_relation": "2*a + b = 0"
      },
      "parameter": "m",
      "path_problem": {
        "type": "two_moving_points_path_minimum",
        "scope": "b",
        "path": "PR+WR"
      },
      "entities": {
        "points": {
          "T": {
            "definition": "axis_x_intercept",
            "of": "parabola",
            "description": "T 是抛物线对称轴与 x 轴的交点"
          },
          "U": {
            "coordinate": ["m", "1"],
            "description": "U(m,1)"
          },
          "V": {
            "definition": "unknown",
            "quadrant": "第四象限",
            "description": "V 在第四象限，且 ∠UTV=90°、TU=TV"
          },
          "W": {
            "definition": "midpoint",
            "of": ["T", "V"],
            "description": "W 为 TV 的中点"
          }
        }
      },
      "relations": [
        {
          "type": "point_on_curve",
          "point": "U",
          "curve": "parabola",
          "description": "U 在抛物线上"
        },
        {
          "type": "point_on_curve",
          "point": "V",
          "curve": "parabola",
          "description": "V 在抛物线上"
        },
        {
          "type": "right_angle_equal_length",
          "scope": "b",
          "angle": ["U", "T", "V"],
          "equal_segments": [["T", "U"], ["T", "V"]],
          "description": "∠UTV=90°，TU=TV"
        },
        {
          "type": "segment_membership",
          "point": "P",
          "segment": ["T", "U"],
          "description": "P 在线段 TU 上"
        },
        {
          "type": "segment_membership",
          "point": "R",
          "segment": ["U", "V"],
          "description": "R 在线段 UV 上"
        },
        {
          "type": "segment_relation",
          "left": "TP",
          "right": "sqrt(2)*RV",
          "description": "TP=√2·RV"
        }
      ],
      "questions": [
        {
          "id": "a",
          "label": "第（A）问",
          "known_coefficients": {
            "a": "2",
            "c": "-5"
          },
          "asks": ["T 的坐标", "抛物线解析式"],
          "goals": [
            {
              "id": "a.axis_point",
              "answer_key": "T",
              "target_path": "$problem.points.T",
              "value_type": "Point",
              "required": true
            },
            {
              "id": "a.parabola",
              "answer_key": "parabola",
              "target_path": "$question.a.outputs.parabola",
              "value_type": "Parabola",
              "required": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "b",
          "label": "第（B）问",
          "givens": ["U(m,1) 在抛物线上", "V 在抛物线上且在第四象限", "∠UTV=90°", "TU=TV"],
          "subquestions": [
            {
              "id": "b_1",
              "label": "第（B）①问",
              "given": "UV=√10",
              "conditions": [
                {
                  "type": "length_squared",
                  "segment": ["U", "V"],
                  "value": "10"
                }
              ],
              "asks": ["抛物线解析式", "PR+WR 的最小值"],
              "goals": [
                {
                  "id": "b_1.parabola",
                  "answer_key": "parabola",
                  "target_path": "$subquestion.b_1.outputs.parabola",
                  "value_type": "Parabola",
                  "required": true
                },
                {
                  "id": "b_1.minimum_value",
                  "answer_key": "min_value",
                  "target_path": "$subquestion.b_1.outputs.min_value",
                  "value_type": "MinimumExpression",
                  "required": true
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "id": "b_2",
              "label": "第（B）②问",
              "given": "PR+WR 的最小值为 5√10/2",
              "conditions": [
                {
                  "type": "minimum_value",
                  "path": "PR+WR",
                  "value": "5*sqrt(10)/2"
                }
              ],
              "asks": ["抛物线解析式", "此时 R 的坐标"],
              "goals": [
                {
                  "id": "b_2.parabola",
                  "answer_key": "parabola",
                  "target_path": "$subquestion.b_2.outputs.parabola",
                  "value_type": "Parabola",
                  "required": true
                },
                {
                  "id": "b_2.intersection",
                  "answer_key": "R",
                  "target_path": "$question.b.points.R",
                  "value_type": "Point",
                  "required": true
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  }
}
